(2321, 'Pfizer HCPP Automation', '1. Worked on DIT-1216 ( Move create-site-legacy to iron ) and DIT-1221( Build all environments for a new legacy sub ).  \n\nI moved the script from https://github.com/pfizer/pfizerhelper/blob/3.x/scripts/python/create-site-legacy.py to https://github.com/pfizer/pfizerhelper/blob/DIT-1216-DIT-1221/pfizerhelper/iron_tasks/create-site-legacy.py.\n\nI found two things which are wrong according to me.\n1. I started a few tests in order to check whether all is ok. For subscription I use *pfhcpportal*.  This site contains different environments, but I had problems with two of them. They are *test2* and *ra*. When I start test for the *test* environment I received *Not Found Error*, \n  1.1. I saw that we have regular expression for *map_branch_env*. \n  1.2. There we have match for test. When script matched my *test2* it sets two variables *branch* and *suffix*. \n  1.3. For *branch* it sets *test* and for suffix - 2\n  1.4. After that we had a dictionary which replace *test* with *test2*\n  1.5. After that the script appends the suffix and I received *test22* instead of *test2*.\n\n2. About the *ra* I receive: *Invalid branch* I think that I receive this because we don''t have match from this in our regular expression.\n\n3. Conversation with Dave''s team.', 21600, 1, '2017-05-19 07:27:18', '2017-05-19 07:27:18', 24, 3, '2017-05-17'),
